Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:04.48,Flashback,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:06.17,Flashback,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.52,Flashback,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think\NI'll be able to do this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:10.19,Flashback,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.95,Flashback,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you will. You're my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:03.35,Show_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mob Psycho\N100
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:10.48,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Discord \N~To Become One~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.48,sign_11461_133_Spirits_and_Such,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits and Such Consultation Office
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:14.81,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the seance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.99,sign_3508_16_Client__Hanako,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Client: {\fs28}Hitoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.33,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.39,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.96,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hitoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:36.86,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought the day would come \Nwhen I got to see your face again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:38.47,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:41.64,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,When did you learn to speak Japanese so well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.05,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, logging out for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:44.75,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:47.58,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm not getting a very good signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:48.97,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Were you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:50.06,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:51.93,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Please call him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:53.65,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.77,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Seances take a lot of concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:03:00.47,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where is your father from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.05,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,New Jersey in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.72,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,All foreign languages will be \Nauto-translated into Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.85,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,This is an advanced technique \Nthat does something-or-other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.81,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,to the wavelength of the spirit's languages,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.71,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,but there will not be an additional fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:16.05,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! But I'm okay with English.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.29,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.05,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hitoshi! How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:27.06,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,It's Japanese... Well, whatever. \NDad, do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.76,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how we used to \Nplay ball when I was a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:32.92,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,And we did that one thing that\Nwas popular on TV back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.90,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Show it to me one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.03,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.53,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:51.24,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,"Cheeseburger Tornado,"\Nthe main character's special move
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:54.41,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,in "Junk Food Fighter Michael,"\Nthe super popular show at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:55.76,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:57.42,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Hitoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:00.44,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Cut to the chase and tell me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:01.91,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.68,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,If being cordial won't work, then screw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.38,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, you shitty old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:11.18,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the password to the hidden safe! \NI know there's a fortune in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:15.19,Main,Ei,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I think the password was my birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:18.40,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap! \NIt's thirteen letters of the alphabet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.36,Main,Hito,0000,0000,0000,,With that money,\NI'll chill for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.86,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.10,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,The password is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.83,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,"GETAJOBYOUBUM"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:38.42,sign_9125_110_Salt_Splash,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Cheeseburger Tornado
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:34.04,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of Reigen's special moves,\Nwhere he uses his whole body like a spring
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:38.42,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and smashes his fist into his opponent's \Nface with a powerful spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:44.00,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! The client's consciousness logged out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:46.39,sign_6760_58_Reception,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Reception
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:46.39,sign_6760_59_Limited_Time_Off,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Limited Time Offer\N{\c&H546370&}Get 3 evil spirit\Nexorcisms for the\Nprice of 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.39,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Did he pass out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:49.85,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... But, well, it was self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.22,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Self-defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.60,Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,What? You look a bit pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:56.63,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,If it's self-defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.75,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,is it okay to shave off someone's hair,\N rip off their clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.19,sign_7163_68_Teru,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Teru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.34,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,destroy their pride, \Nmake them lose their friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:05.33,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,and destroy the school they go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:10.16,Main,Re,0000,0000,0000,,How can you do that much in self-defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:14.73,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when my psychic powers\Ngo out of control...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:17.42,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,And it happens when I'm unconscious, to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.76,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want these powers anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:23.55,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, they're of use to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.23,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:29.47,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Think of all of the clients \Nyou helped with those powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.27,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just focus on the negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.93,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about how you use knives, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.76,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't suppress yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:39.72,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who holds the keys\Nto maximizing your potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:40.77,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.68,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.28,Main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:48.68,Main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow leader system?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.53,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:53.21,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,I completely lost to that\Nshadow leader named Hanazawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:56.48,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,but the guy who beat him \Nis from Salt Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.29,Main,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,Someone that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:02.29,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We're gonna have him \Nbe our shadow leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.17,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who caused the supernatural\Nincident at Black Vinegar Middle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.58,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.74,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,You're basically the only person\Nwho could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.85,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but according to the rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.56,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,There's a kid at Black Vinegar Middle\Nwho easily throws people around, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.41,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's an esper just like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:25.15,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,And then you two met at Black \NVinegar Middle School, and fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.53,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,An esper battle! \NThat's what happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:28.82,Italics,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Twitch, twitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.92,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.08,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for today, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:38.41,Main,Meza,0000,0000,0000,,But someday, you're definitely \Ngoing to tell me all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:42.92,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Mob-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:45.25,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that wasn't the work of aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.55,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,And that aside, there are \Nespers other than yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.06,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.41,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,You can find them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.25,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I've only met one other in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:01.02,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. What about your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:01.85,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:05.54,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I don't \Nsense anything from my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:09.32,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,But that's because his powers\Nare spiritual, not psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:10.86,sign_10217_111_ESP_Powers,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Psychic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.86,sign_10259_112_Spiritual_Powers,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.86,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of rule is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:13.92,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.\NLet's go on a date after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:14.71,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.64,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to find other \Ntelepathic people together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:22.04,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,And then take our first step toward \Nconnecting with outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.25,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not in the Telepathy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:28.54,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Black Vinegar Middle School's shadow leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:32.66,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to him.\NThat guy had some nice muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:35.13,Main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then who beat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.64,Main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,It was someone from your club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:40.43,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,He's a gentleman who \Nusually dislikes violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:43.60,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Do not involve him in this. Begone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.31,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Tch. Damn that Musashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:48.53,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.07,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:53.57,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,You were picked on by the guys from Black \NVinegar Middle School last week, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:57.01,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,That was all my fault. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.03,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:59.79,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the small stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.64,Main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kageyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.89,Main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Tenga-san's an idiot,\Nso he can't explain things proper—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:04.79,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.29,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.06,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to him. Stay out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.85,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:16.49,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,That will be all of the student council's\Nactivities for this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.80,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right, President Kamuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.27,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:25.68,sign_12019_141_Salt_Middle_Scho,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,426)}Salt Middle School\NStudent Council President:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:25.68,sign_12019_142_Kamuro_Shinji,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,426)}Kamuro\NShinji
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:26.09,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad, but we need \Nsomething with more impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.80,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so, \Nfirst-year, Kageyama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:32.36,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,You rank as one of the smartest in the nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.82,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,so I want to hear your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:36.87,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Right... In our school,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.74,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,there are students known as delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:45.12,sign_12462_148_Undecided_Box,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Pending\NBox
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:43.69,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,If the student council could reprimand them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:46.70,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'd be able to \Ncreate a peaceful school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:49.38,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,I see... a peaceful school, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:53.72,sign_12693_153_Delinquents_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,980)}Disciplining Delinquents
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:52.26,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,That's great. Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:57.34,Italics,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make it a comfortable \Nenvironment for my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.35,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:05.14,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. I guess there was a \Npoint in waiting around after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.48,sign_13081_157_Awakening_Lab_Mi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Awakening Lab\NMitsuura Kenji
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.48,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Here are my credentials.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.25,Italics,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Awakening Lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.61,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Kageyama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:17.70,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why not try to amplify your psychic powers\Nat my research facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:20.82,Italics,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,He's got me confused with Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.42,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Tome-san. That person—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.87,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is he an esper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:28.33,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just thought he had \Na very unique hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.09,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.68,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.09,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.93,sign_13081_157_Awakening_Lab_Mi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Awakening Lab\NMitsuura Kenji
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.93,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Kageyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:43.56,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Vice President Tokugawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.37,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Loitering, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:49.30,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even people like you \Nfeel like doing that at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:53.53,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Like me? I'm just a normal middle school \Nstudent you can find anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.88,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Totally simple and normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:10:01.08,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,You won't find a totally simple and normal\Nmiddle schooler anywhere on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:05.91,Main,Tku,0000,0000,0000,,But, for whatever reason, you want to\Nbe one and are trying to act the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.96,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I understand \Nwhat you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:12.60,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Despite having abilities that always\Nmake you the center of attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:16.97,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,you try to play the minor role\Nand let others have the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.14,Main,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to act like your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.48,Main,Saga,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Kageyama-kun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.78,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:40.03,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're starting to\Nbuild up some stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:40.41,sign_15346_185_Progress_Towards,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Progress Towards
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:40.78,sign_15355_186_Mob_s_Explosion,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mob's Explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.03,Mob's_Explosion,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Progress Toward Mob's Explosion: {\c&HFAFFCA&}4{\c&HFFFFFF&}%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:51.54,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,Awakening Lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.16,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,This place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.80,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly just a normal\Napartment complex—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:54.80,sign_15676_190_Fortress_Seasoni,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fortress\NSeasoning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:56.26,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kageyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.51,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:01.61,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,There's no research facility here.\NYou lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.55,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:06.98,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.97,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,to the Awakening Lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:14.10,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.36,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I bought an apartment complex\Nand remodeled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:20.07,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've hired the front runners in\Nneural science and engineering,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.63,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,and we do research here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:25.59,Main,Uy,0000,0000,0000,,The esper kids are on the floor above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.83,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.87,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there are other people just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.63,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.38,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Another guy with a weird haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:38.74,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,That's an adult esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:45.34,Italics,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling? It's kind of sickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:49.79,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tome-san. I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:53.31,Main,Tome,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Mob-kun! Isn't that \Nhairstyle super weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.23,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:12:01.88,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Real espers that the Mitsuura Group\Nworked hard to bring together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:04.49,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,First is Hoshino Takeshi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.99,sign_17317_213_Hoshino_Takeshi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,393)}Hoshino\NTakeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.62,Main,Hosh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.58,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He has psychokinetic powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:17.21,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to be amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.46,sign_17686_218_Kurosaki_Rei,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,305)}Kurosaki\NRei
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.90,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we have Kurosaki Rei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:25.76,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Her powers of clairvoyance allow her\Nto pick the one correct card out of ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.84,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Her efficiency rate is 62%!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:32.48,Main,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I was right again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.85,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:36.20,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we have Asahi Go-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.90,sign_18082_224_Asahi_Go,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(447,396)}Asahi\NGo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:38.95,Main,Go,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, my pyrokinesis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.11,Main,Go,0000,0000,0000,,Ignite!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:41.65,Main,Go,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:44.11,Main,Go,0000,0000,0000,,Ignite! Ignite!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:46.74,Main,Go,0000,0000,0000,,Ig—There we go! Oh, it went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.58,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He uses pyrokinesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.12,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,And is less useful than a 100-yen lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.66,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Shiratori brothers: \NDaichi-kun and Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.25,sign_18475_234_Shiratori,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(396,353)}Shiratori
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.25,sign_18475_235_Daichi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(396,353)}Daichi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.25,sign_18475_236_Kaito,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(396,353)}Kaito
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:58.90,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They're telepaths who can communicate\Nwith each other, even when they're apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.25,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,And less useful than email.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:04.47,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kageyama Shigeo-kun. Be nice to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.81,Main,Hoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:06.68,Main,Kuro,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.54,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,Did Mitsuura-san do something to all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.65,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's rather rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:16.36,Main,Hoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. That old man is just \Nfascinated with psychic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.06,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:22.53,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the son of a very wealthy family, \Nbut I'm not anyone special.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:26.82,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in doing anything to make \Nadvancements in society or science.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.74,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to become an esper myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:33.00,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So I made a research facility. That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.59,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,This is a childish pipe dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.00,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,but if he's able to make that \Nhappen, I'd be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.88,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to rise to my standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.26,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shinji. You're finally home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.26,sign_19763_254_Kamuro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kamuro
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:50.56,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Student council again? Make sure \Nyou don't fool around too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.81,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san was the student\Ncouncil president, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.69,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But Takuya was also good in his studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:01.31,Main,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. I'm embarrassed, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.83,Main,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't even hit a\Nstandardized score of 70 yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.37,Main,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really my younger brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.77,Main,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,You suck at violin, drawing, \Ncalligraphy, and have no talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:09.37,Main,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,so you became the student \Ncouncil president, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.28,Main,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you should have time to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.87,Main,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,How much are you going to \Ndisappoint Mom and Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:14.53,Main,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Elites like—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:25.64,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:29.05,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, you need to really \Nfix that habit of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.80,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,But it just bends on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:33.85,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, a fart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.64,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop that! We're eating dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.94,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Shige, you need to be more like Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.15,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:44.29,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsu is much more talented than I am\Nand doesn't do anything weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.68,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kageyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:01.08,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, President? \NWhy did you call me here so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.34,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,This is a girl's recorder bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:07.23,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think is inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.30,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,A girl's recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:10.88,Main,kamu,0000,0000,0000,,Correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:12.19,Main,rits,0000,0000,0000,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:14.18,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,It's long, so let's just take this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:18.19,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.47,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing? \NWhy, spring cleaning, Kageyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:23.17,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,Spring cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.61,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,You said it yourself, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.99,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,"There is trash called \Ndelinquents in our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.49,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,The student council should \Nget rid of them."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.98,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,I never said anything that extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:34.67,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't twist my words—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.41,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Kageyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:41.99,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,This is the desk of our school's biggest \Npiece of trash, Onigawara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:47.94,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you serious, President? \NWhy would an elite like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:49.30,Main,Kam,0000,0000,0000,,An elite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:54.30,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,That's just an imaginary persona \Nthat someone labeled me with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.88,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,You've realized it, too, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:16:01.06,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,That the praise others lavish upon you\Ndoesn't actually fit who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.58,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,Come, help me, Kageyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:11.20,Flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You got another perfect score on your test?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:12.25,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:16.08,Flashback,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsu is much more talented than I am\Nand doesn't do anything weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.38,Flashback,Toku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to act like your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.12,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,Even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.45,Flashback,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think \NI'll be able to do this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.17,Flashback,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.82,Flashback,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you will. You're my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:30.00,Flashback,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:41.75,Main,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.90,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we made it to the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.92,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some good muscles \Non you, Onigawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:54.68,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... You called me out early,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:58.07,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought you were going to tell me\Nwho the shadow leader is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:03.58,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that pain and how \Ngood it feels, Onigawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:07.69,Main,Goda,0000,0000,0000,,The one you're looking for is \Nalso fighting with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:10.04,Main,God,0000,0000,0000,,So you should change, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.51,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:15.87,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.72,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,There's been an incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.09,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:21.95,Main,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.35,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Can the student council \Ndo anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.04,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:25.27,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,We're so grossed out, there's no way\Nwe can take classes normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.46,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:32.62,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,I promise that the student council \Nwill find the culprit and stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:35.83,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,You open up Onigawara's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.78,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to inspect everyone's belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.54,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If they get caught like this,\Nthey must be pretty stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.67,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the teacher's not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:51.05,Italics,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to ruin my record \Nof never being late or absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.39,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Onigawara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:54.92,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,You seem out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:59.60,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,What's Kamuro doing here? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:01.53,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:02.91,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,I found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.79,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,They were all in Onigawara-san's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.48,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?\NWhy are you going through my desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.11,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you, Onigawara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.87,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:15.65,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.07,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell just said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.28,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.66,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did you find in my desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:28.96,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,We found all of the girls' missing \Nrecorder pieces in your desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.05,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you were going to lick \Nthem when no one was looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.93,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pervert, Onigawara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:36.55,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,What? Kamuro, don't make me punch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:39.80,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,There's still time! Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:45.86,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:48.35,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really look like someone who'd do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:51.92,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,You are violent with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.40,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,That's reason enough not to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.48,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:19:00.86,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, yeah! If I really wanted to lick them, \NI would take them out of the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:03.36,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Only an idiot would leave them in his desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:05.45,Main,Amu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're an idiot, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:10.08,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being unreasonable, Kamuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.99,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,There were some in his bag, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.80,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,So you had taken a number of them home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:19.93,Italics,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,My school bag... \NI left it wide open in my locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:24.18,Italics,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama-kun, you even put some in \Nhis bag? You're all into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.76,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:27.85,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Stop snooping around my bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.39,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to resort to violence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.06,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.33,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You're taking it out on a first-year?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:33.40,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Poor Kageyama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:33.03,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,So gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:36.47,Main,Ids,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't Tenga the Demon, \Nbut Tenga the Recorder Licker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.21,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,So violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.71,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I have to disinfect mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.32,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Give us back our recorders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:35.99,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:36.69,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.08,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.25,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:55.34,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Pervert! Pervert! Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:46.58,Main,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:49.33,Main,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,Run, everyone! The pervert's mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.67,Italics,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,No... No! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:02.33,Italics,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't... Isn't there someone \Nwho'll take my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:03.45,Flashback,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.35,Flashback,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll marry you when I get older, Tenga-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.77,Flashback,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.19,Italics,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:17.14,Italics,Oni,0000,0000,0000,,You believe me, don't you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:18.69,Main,Mari,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.53,sign_29230_387_Gross,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Gross
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:32.50,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're so gross, you perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:36.52,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,On this day, after two years of hard work,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:41.02,Narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Onigawara Tenga's perfect \Nattendance record was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.01,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:51.23,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be down. Everyone has bad days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:55.45,Flashback,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see, Kageyama-kun? \NOnigawara's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:59.23,Flashback,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,The despair of not being able \Nto solve something by fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:02.03,Flashback,Kamu,0000,0000,0000,,He's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:10.20,Main,Ritsu,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:12.76,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:13.53,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.53,0:21:16.31,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,I actually don't have psychic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.13,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on... Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:19.98,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.82,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Mob's little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.88,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're giving me\Nthe cold shoulder as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:35.73,Main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,What are you wandering around\Nnear my house for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:41.44,Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,I got a request to exorcise a creepy ghost\Nthat's been showing up in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.75,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Want to help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:47.43,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,No. Unlike my brother,\NI don't have any special powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:50.62,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Really? But you're Mob's little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:56.85,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you exorcise this ghost yourself?\N Aren't you a psychic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:01.09,Main,Hosh,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama quit by throwing a spoon?\NNot a towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:05.15,Main,Hosh,0000,0000,0000,,He's got quite the sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:08.74,Main,Hoshi,0000,0000,0000,,But as far as I can see, \Nhe doesn't have much talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:09.74,Main,Gy,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:11.98,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:15.84,Main,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.65,sign_32036_416_Kageyama,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kageyama
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:17.68,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:23.17,Italics,Rits,0000,0000,0000,,It's not... a balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:23:58.83,Main_Preview,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsu continues to go wild \Nby pairing up with Dimple.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:01.32,Main_Preview,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,And then the gang leader alliance\Nmakes its move.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:03.64,Main_Preview,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, some scary people \Ntry to make Mob buy a vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.64,0:24:05.10,Main_Preview,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Both brothers are in huge trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.10,0:24:06.61,Main_Preview,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Mob Psycho 100{\i0} Episode 7:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:08.51,Main_Preview,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,"Exaltation \N~I've Obtained Loss~"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.51,0:24:10.97,sign_34730_425_Exaltation___I_v,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Exaltation \N~I've Obtained Loss~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.51,0:24:10.97,Main_Preview,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Illegal downloads? \NYou're going to be cursed.
